      • setStereoisomerType

        public StereoisomerSettings setStereoisomerType(EnumSet<StereoisomerSettings.StereoisomerType> types)
        Sets which types of stereoiseomers should be generated. Available values:
        • TETRAHEDRAL : tetrahedral stereoisomers are generated
        • CISTRANS : double bond stereoisomers are generated
        Parameters:
        types - are the stereoisomerism types (represented by an enumset)
